data.description: Four bedrooms and three bathrooms in this great Ellerbe Road Estates home. Remote master bedroom. Remote guest suite. And, two remote bedrooms and a bathroom. This 2514-square-foot home sits on the corner lot of a cul-de-sac. The front room is a large living and dining room. There is also a family room with a cathedral ceiling, a wood-burning fireplace, built-ins, and a wet bar. Call for your tour today.
